{
  "id": "nn_mpr5nvzx_yzh5nendb",
  "title": "Arrays basic",
  "content": "\n\n<div style=\"background-color:#121314\"><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\"># DSA</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\"># 📌 PHASE 1 — ARRAY BASICS &amp; LARGEST ELEMENT</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔹 What is Array (DS)?</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Array is a </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**DS (Data Structure)**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> which store </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**similar element**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Agar yeh DS ek particular type ka hai</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">toh </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**similar type hona chahiye**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">chahe </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**integer ho, char ho, string ho, pair ho**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Array looks like</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">[ ][ ][ ]</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔹 Declaration of Array</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### In C / C++</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```cpp</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">[</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">6</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">];</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### In Java</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```java</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#4ec9b0\">int</span><span style=\"color:#ffa657\"> </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">[] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=newarr[</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">6</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">];</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> jab aap yeh likh dete ho toh kya hota hai ki</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**size 6 ka array create hota hai**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> agar </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**inside main**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> declare kiya → </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**garbage values**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> aati hain</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> agar </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**global**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> declare kiya → </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**0 se filled hota hai**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> (C++)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Java me bhi default value </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**0 hoti hai**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Python ka sure nahi 😅</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### 📝 NOTE (Correction)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Java me bhi </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**garbage values nahi hoti**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">, default value </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**0 hoti hai**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Python me traditional array nahi hota, list hoti hai (dynamic)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔹 Maximum Size of Array</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Inside </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">`int main()`</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`10^6`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Global array**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`10^7`</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### 📝 NOTE (Correction)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Yeh </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**stack vs heap limitation**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> ki wajah se hota hai.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Global arrays heap/static memory me jaate hain.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔹 Accessing an Array</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Array ko access karne ke liye </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**index**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> use hota hai.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> index starts from </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**0 to n-1**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```cpp</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">for</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> i =</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">0</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">; i &lt; n; i++) </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">{</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#d2a8ff\">print</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">(arr[i]);</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">}</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔹 Where is Array Stored in Memory?</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Array </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**computer memory**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> me store hota hai.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> maan lo array ka </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**first block random x location**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> pe hai</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> hume x pata hota hai</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> 0th index → x</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> 1st index → x + 1</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> 2nd index → x + 2</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Array </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**continuous memory**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> me store hota hai.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\"># 🔥 LARGEST ELEMENT IN AN ARRAY</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Hum </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**direct solution nahi denge**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">,</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">interview ko </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**drive karna hai**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Flow hoga:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">👉 </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Brute → Better → Optimal**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## Example</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">arr[] = [3, 2, 1, 5, 2]</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔹 Brute Force Approach</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Idea:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Array ko sort karo**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Last element pick karo**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```cpp</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">largest = </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">[n-</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">1</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">];</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### Complexity</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Sorting → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n log n)`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Space → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(1)`</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> (kuch naya nahi bana rahe)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔹 Optimal Approach</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Idea:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> First element ko </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**largest maan lo**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Traverse karo</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Agar koi bada mil jaye → largest update</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```cpp</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">largest = </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">[</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">0</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">];</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">for</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> i =</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">0</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">; i &lt; n; i++) </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">{</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">if</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">(arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> largest) {</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; largest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i];</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">}</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#d2a8ff\">print</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">(largest);</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### Complexity</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Time:**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n)`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Optimise ho gaya 🎯</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">👉 </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Next Phase me cover karenge:**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Second Largest</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Second Smallest</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Check if array sorted</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Remove duplicates (Brute → Optimal)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Bolo </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Phase 2 chalu karein? 💪**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">next</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Perfect 👍</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">👉 </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**PHASE 2: Second Largest, Second Smallest, Check Sorted Array**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">(Again reminder: </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**aapke words, language, flow same rakhe gaye hain**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">, bas structure + spelling + syntax clean kiya hai.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Galat cheez ke niche </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**NOTE**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> diya hai.)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\"># 📌 PHASE 2 — SECOND LARGEST / SECOND SMALLEST / CHECK SORTED</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔥 SECOND LARGEST ELEMENT IN ARRAY</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Interview me </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**second largest**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> ya </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**second smallest**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> dono puch sakte hain.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### 🔹 Brute Force Approach</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Idea:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Array ko </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**sort**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> kar do</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`arr[n-2]`</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> output hoga</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Par dikkat yeh hai 👇</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">kya pata </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**saare element same ho**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">ya last ke </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**4–5 same ho**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Example:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">1 2 4 5 7 7</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`largest = arr[n-1]`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`n-1`</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> se peeche traverse karo</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> jo </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**largest ke barabar nahi ho**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> → wahi second largest</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```cpp</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">largest = </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">[n-</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">1</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">];</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">for</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> i = n-</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">2</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">; i &gt;=</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">0</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">; i--) </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">{</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">if</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">(arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">!=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> largest) {</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; secondLargest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i];</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">break</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">;</span><span style=\"color:#8b949e\">// necessary kyuki aage ka koi fayda nahi</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">}</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### Worst Case</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">1 7 7 7 7 7</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> poora traverse karna padega</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### Complexity</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Sorting → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n log n)`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Loop → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n)`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Total → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n log n + n)`</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔹 Better Approach (2 Pass)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Idea:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">1.</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**First pass**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> → largest nikaalo</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">2.</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Second pass**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> → second largest nikaalo</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Example:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">1 2 4 7 7 5</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> largest = 7</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> secondLargest = -1 (maan liya array me positives hain)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Condition:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> element </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**largest se chota ho**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> element </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**secondLargest se bada ho**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```cpp</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">largest = </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">[</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">0</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">];</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#8b949e\">// First pass</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">for</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> i =</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">0</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">; i &lt; n; i++) </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">{</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">if</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">(arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> largest) {</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; largest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i];</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">}</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">secondLargest =-</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">1</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">;</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#8b949e\">// Second pass</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">for</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> i =</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">0</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">; i &lt; n; i++) </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">{</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">if</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">(arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> secondLargest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&amp;&amp;</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">!=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> largest) {</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; secondLargest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i];</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">}</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### Complexity</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> First pass → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n)`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Second pass → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n)`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Total → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(2n)`</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> ≈ </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n)`</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔹 Optimal Approach (Single Pass)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Idea:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**largest**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> aur </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**secondLargest**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> dono saath manage karo</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Example:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">1, 2, 4, 7, 7, 5</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Steps:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> first element → largest</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> secondLargest ko </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**bahut chota**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> maan lo</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Logic:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> agar koi element </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**largest se bada**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> ho</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; → secondLargest = largest</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; → largest = current element</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> agar element </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**largest se chota**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> ho</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; aur </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**secondLargest se bada**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> ho</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; → secondLargest update</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```cpp</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">largest = </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">[</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">0</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">];</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">slargest =-</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">1</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">;</span><span style=\"color:#8b949e\">// agar negative values ho sakti hain toh INT_MIN</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">for</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> i =</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">1</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">; i &lt; n; i++) </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">{</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">if</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">(arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> largest) {</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; slargest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> largest;</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; largest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i];</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#d2a8ff\">elseif</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">(arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> largest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&amp;&amp;</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> slargest) {</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; slargest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i];</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">}</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">return</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> slargest;</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Example:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">8 7 5 6 7 8 9</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔥 SECOND SMALLEST ELEMENT</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Same logic bas </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**ulta**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> smallest = first element</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> ssmallest = </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**INT_MAX**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```cpp</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">smallest = </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">arr</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">[</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">0</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">];</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">ssmallest = INT_MAX;</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">for</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> i =</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">1</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">; i &lt; n; i++) </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">{</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">if</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">(arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> smallest) {</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ssmallest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> smallest;</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; smallest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i];</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#d2a8ff\">elseif</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">(arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> smallest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&amp;&amp;</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> ssmallest) {</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ssmallest </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i];</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">}</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### Complexity</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Time:**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n)`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Single pass**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Better than better solution 😎</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔍 CHECK IF ARRAY IS SORTED</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Example:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">[1, 2, 3, 3, 4] → sorted</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">[1, 2, 1, 3, 4] →not sorted</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Isme </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**brute / better / optimal**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> ki koi zarurat nahi</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Simple logic hai.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Idea:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> har element ko </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**previous se compare**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> karo</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> agar kahin bhi chota mil gaya → not sorted</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```cpp</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">for</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> i =</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">1</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">; i &lt; n; i++) </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">{</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">if</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">(arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&gt;=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">-</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">1</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">]) {</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#8b949e\">// kuch nahi karo</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">else</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> {</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">returnfalse;</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">}</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">returntrue;</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### Explanation</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> agar loop poora chal gaya</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; matlab </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**koi dikkat nahi aayi**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> isliye last me </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`return true`</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">👉 </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Next Phase me aayega:**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Remove duplicates from sorted array</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Brute → Optimal (Two Pointer)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\"># 📌 PHASE 3 — REMOVE DUPLICATES (IN-PLACE)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔥 Problem Statement</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Sorted array diya hai, </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**duplicates remove karne hain in-place**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Example:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">arr = [1,1,2,2,2,3,3]</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Output:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">arr = [1,2,3, _, _, _, _]</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> first </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**unique elements starting me aane chahiye**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> baaki jagah </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**kuch bhi ho sakta hai**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**new array nahi banana**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> same array use karna hai</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Agar </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**3 unique elements hain**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">toh </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**starting ke 3 index**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> pe hi hone chahiye.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔹 Brute Force Approach</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Idea:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> “unique chahiye mujhe”</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> mere dimag me </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**set**</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> aa raha hai</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> set duplicate allow nahi karta</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> array traverse karo</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> set me insert karo</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```cpp</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">set&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">&gt; st;</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">for</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> i =</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">0</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">; i &lt; n; i++) </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">{</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; st.</span><span style=\"color:#d2a8ff\">insert</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">(arr[i]);</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">}</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Ab set me </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**sirf unique elements**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> hain.</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Ab wapas array me daalna hai 👇</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```cpp</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> index =</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">0</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">;</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">for</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">auto</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> it : st) </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">{</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; arr[index] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> it;</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; index</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">++</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">;</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">}</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### Complexity</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> set insertion → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n log n)`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> array overwrite → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n)`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> total → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n log n + n)`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> space → </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n)`</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> (extra set use hua)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### 📝 NOTE</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Problem ne bola tha </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**in-place**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">,</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; lekin yahan </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**extra space**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> use ho rahi hai</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; isliye interview me yeh </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**optimal nahi maana jaata**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔹 Optimal Approach (Two Pointer)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Yeh </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**important interview solution**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> hai 🔥</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Given:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">arr = [1,1,2,2,2,3,3]</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### Idea (aapke words me):</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> array </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**sorted hai**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> (bahut important)</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> ek pointer hoga jo </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**unique element ko point karega**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> dusra pointer aage jaa ke </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**naya element dhundega**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> jo first pointer hai</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> wo initially </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`arr[0]`</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> pe hoga</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> aur wo dhundega ki</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> </span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> “mere jaisa element kaha nahi mil raha”</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#6a9955\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#7ee787\"> </span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Jaha </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**different element milega**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">waha usko </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**next position pe daal denge**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### Two Pointer Explanation</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`i`</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> → unique element ka index</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`j`</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> → traversal ke liye</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Start:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">i =0</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Loop:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```cpp</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">for</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#ff7b72\">int</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\"> j =</span><span style=\"color:#b5cea8\">1</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">; j &lt; n; j++) </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">{</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c586c0\">if</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">(arr[j] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">!=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[i]) {</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; i</span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">++</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">;</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; arr[i] </span><span style=\"color:#d4d4d4\">=</span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\"> arr[j];</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">}</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### Final Result</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> array ke </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**0 se i tak**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> → unique elements</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> total unique elements = </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`i + 1`</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">### Example Dry Run</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">arr = [1,1,2,2,2,3,3]</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">i =0</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> j=1 → same (1==1) → ignore</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> j=2 → different (2!=1) → i=1 → arr[</span><span style=\"color:#a5d6ff\">1</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">]=2</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> j=3 → same → ignore</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> j=4 → same → ignore</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> j=5 → different → i=2 → arr[</span><span style=\"color:#a5d6ff\">2</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">]=3</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> j=6 → same → ignore</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Final array:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">[1, 2, 3, x, x, x, x]</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">Unique count:</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">i +1 =3</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">```</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## 🔹 Complexity (Optimal)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Time:**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(n)`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Space:**</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"color:#79c0ff\">`O(1)`</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Single pass**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Fully </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**in-place**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\">🔥 This is the </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**best solution**</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">---</span></div><br><div><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#79c0ff\">## ✅ Summary (Interview Friendly)</span></div><br><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Sorted array hai → </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**Two Pointer**</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> Extra space allowed → set</span></div><div><span style=\"color:#ffa657\">-</span><span style=\"color:#bbbebf\"> In-place chahiye → </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#c9d1d9\">**optimal solution use karo**</span></div></div>\n\n",
